OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FControversial radio        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsculpture coming to Cardiff
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A controversial four-metre wooden      
OL,6, sculpture to mark the first radio      
OL,7, broadcast is to be erected in Cardiff. 
OL,9,FThe first radio signal of its kind was 
OL,10,Ftransmitted by Guglielmo Marconi       
OL,11,Fbetween nearby Lavernock Point and Flat
OL,12,FHolm island in 1897.                   
OL,14,FBut earlier this year there were calls 
OL,15,Fto scrap the sculpture after           
OL,16,Fcouncillors learned of Marconi's       
OL,17,Ffascist links.                         
OL,19,FCardiff Council said there will be no  
OL,20,Freference to Marconi on the sculpture. 
